    "en": {
      "title": "Bus fares increase by 30 percent",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The bus owners have requested for a 30 percent increase in bus fares and a minimum fare of 40 rupees from July 1, said Dr. Thilan Miranda, Director General of the National Transport Commission.",
        "The National Transport Commission (NTC) will consider the request and approve it tomorrow (29), Miranda said.",
        "The request was made during a discussion between Transport Minister Dr. Bandula Gunawardena, officials of the National Transport Commission and bus associations this afternoon (28), Miranda said."
      ],
